      "span_text": "Cows (n = 425 for each time point) at the mid luteal phase (days 10-12) were injected with PGF 2a in intramuscular (0 h) (0.5 mg of cloprostenol, 2.0 mL of Estrumate TM , Essex Tierarznei, Munich, Germany), and ovaries were collected by ovariectomy [CITATION_1] through the vagina at 0 ( = before PGF 2a injection), 5, 15, and 30 min and 2 and 12 h.",
